text.tspan: Highly organised and disciplined pharmacy leader with excellent communication and conflict
resolution skills. Competent in managing supplies, reviewing service quality, and maintaining patient
confidentiality and satisfaction. Skilled at ordering, storing, and preparing medications for customer
use. Accomplished in increasing customer satisfaction while improving controls, team operations,
and loss prevention strategies. Knowledgeable in preparing special compounds.
Checked more than 30 patient orders against histories each day,
assessed insurance coverage and counted out medicines.
Provided patient counselling regarding OTC medications.
Managed weekly schedules and requests for leave.
Used pharmacy software Meditab to verify prescription and insurance
Compounded and prepared medications according to prescription
orders for more than 160 prescriptions every week.
